The paper deals with the problem of secret sharing over a Gaussian wiretap channel, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT) and cryptography (cs.CR). The use of LDPC codes is a common technique in coding theory (cs.CC) and communication systems (cs.MM). The paper also mentions the use of a public channel for exchanging messages, which is a topic in secure communication (cs.SI).
